{"tid":127193,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"疑學業困擾 15歲男生自縊命危","createTime":"2017-02-20T02:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T02:00:04.000Z","uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0569cd353ea55e611757f24992547bc82f4b8ac4","tid":127193,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:18:00.000Z","msg":"【東方日報專訊】【本報訊】十五歲中學男生疑不堪學業困擾，昨午在油塘住鯉魚門邨寓所自縊，幸及時被母親發現報警，送院搶救後情況殆危。今次是一個月內第六宗學生自殺事件，有關注青少年問題專家勸喻：「挫折過後，雨過天青，彩虹再現。」人生不要看得太灰。<br />\n<br />\n月內第六宗學生自殺<br />\n<br />\n現場鯉魚門邨鯉生樓一單位，命危姓吳男生，與家人同住上址。昨中午十二時許，吳母（四十三歲）發現兒子用繩索吊頸，慌忙剪斷繩索及報警，救護車趕至將已陷昏迷的吳送院，，經搶救後需要在深切治療病房留醫，情況危殆。警方在場調查時，並用警車接載兩名男女親友往醫院，其中女親友極度傷心需警員攙扶。警方向事主家人了解後，獲知吳受到學業問題困擾，不排除因此尋死。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港家庭及事業發展服務訓練總監司徒漢明指出，青少年遇挫折覺得痛苦，才會走上不歸路，但其實人生任何階段都會有挫折及困難，只要我們相信挫折過後必定雨過天青，彩虹也會再現，就不會將困難及人生睇得太灰。另外，讀書成績不好不代表無前途，事實上人生不只是讀書一個舞台，還有其他舞台讓大家去發揮。當然，青少年也需裝備自己，提升個人情緒智商（EQ），懂得面對困難時去渲洩及求助，人生會愈活愈精彩。</span>"},{"pid":"d401fa2d138bdeacab8cf746a74ce90f2646333c","tid":127193,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺上以前讀書果陣都冇而家咁辛苦"},{"pid":"01ecca3160691aaaea779c6b978a6a18d98319e0","tid":127193,"uid":18082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"而家啲學生係咪好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n以前都係al ce放榜先有一單因學業自殺<br />\n<br />\n而家15歲已經諗住死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08b7431849a0c6f2767070f02e7a84b4f4c283c","tid":127193,"uid":82121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺上以前讀書果陣都冇而家咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>佢地話而家d細路唔捱得，又冇生涯規劃呀嘛</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人命嚟㗎diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對政府嚟講可能只係少咗一個未來嘅勞動力，先講得出啲咁冷血嘅說話，對人地屋企人朋友係冇咗忽肉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳克儉幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c651a47fa8b8f4a646f4a479a94cff89afa835f9","tid":127193,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"當一個城市變成咁，就算幾有錢都無用"},{"pid":"dbd74ff87588be418c743d266137589fbf177583","tid":127193,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"以前讀中學考衰咗都冇諗過去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家啲學校究竟質咗幾多quiz test exam功課畀學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家長又係咪又迫緊仔女補習同學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲老師又有幾多個真係會關心同學仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係埋牙就&ldquo;你哋今次唔好考衰，唔好影衰我呀&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ac66d226e11221b2dd5008d29ae137012acd5ebb","tid":127193,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"對住個港共政權仲邊有明天<br />\n下世唔好做香港人<br />\n上車無望嘅AL撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw點解係影視台"},{"pid":"c66a5610118af7f34788ecde5d2e36af323c1335","tid":127193,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e826f8127be5de90c3e5c5fafc9394de6cc6638b","tid":127193,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"疑學業困擾都懶到學業問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf62e318bdcfc85af2b43a00e2c4c203595c98fb","tid":127193,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">疑</span>學業困擾都懶到學業問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}